{"tid":1185861,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]大家而家即刻打開你地嘅instagram","createTime":"2019-06-04T13:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T15:47:57.000Z","uid":60381,"like":33,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81e3290f2df605b598011c8ed3a301d7b0fb1622","tid":1185861,"uid":60381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:53:17.000Z","msg":"sorry昆左你地入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知放咩台好<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好睇少社交媒體嘅影響力<br />\n即使係小小一個post/story都好有傳播力<br />\n<br />\n細佬我生活社交都正常<br />\n平時啲story都有400人左右睇過<br />\n當中計唔到有幾多人有認真睇<br />\n但我而家keep住每日都出一個story<br />\n講下啲政治歷史 share下啲新聞post<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">包括叫人6月9號上街 提下班豬仔frd六四死好多人</span><br />\n雖然我地係普通市民 寂寂無名<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">但係每一個人都係一場運動嘅重要力量</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好怕自己post嘅嘢冇人睇<br />\n只要保住恆心每日都post少少嘢<br />\n黑底白字大大隻<br />\n就算係好快一秒碌過個post<br />\n都會望到下啲字 已經傳播到信息<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今次我地6月9號一定要塞爆成個港島</span></span><br />\n<br />\n共勉之 街頭見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1496629a585ca3f08c3b87f81a01d83283b2414","tid":1185861,"uid":60381,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"每日比400人睇到 <span style=\"color: red;\">6月9號要上街</span><br />\n作用其實好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6641ddd392fd17241970594db24c97e46da7e02c","tid":1185861,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"我ig得5條友follow"},{"pid":"aa485fcb36dd9f8c1135fc57157ab4b450807ee6","tid":1185861,"uid":60381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6641ddd392fd17241970594db24c97e46da7e02c","tid":1185861,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"我ig得5條友follow"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"咁我地一齊去擺街站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c